{"tid":1995972,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓市升溫】南豐廣場上車客撻定 業主重售多賺18萬","createTime":"2020-04-30T16:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T04:12:03.000Z","uid":267488,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"94de1e5f9dcc5a43c501e9d40c83fe3694487bcf","tid":1995972,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:06:42.000Z","msg":"隨着疫情緩和及購買力逐漸釋放，本港樓市急速升溫。將軍澳南豐廣場有單位一個月內賣兩次。美聯物業黃少明稱，南豐廣場5座低層G室兩房戶，實用面積375方呎，本月10日原以608萬元售出，買家為上車客，因疫情關係，睇淡後市，決定撻定20萬元離場。單位同月27日重新放盤，3日內再獲承接，成交價606萬元。雖然樓價賣平2萬元，但計及殺定，業主料多賺18萬元。新買家亦為上車客，在市場睇樓超過一年。<br />\n<br />\n連登仔幾時先攬炒成功呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffad7c3d3cc47995879a2e999647032a68cc8efb","tid":1995972,"uid":188026,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:26:51.000Z","msg":"三年後起碼上到650"},{"pid":"dafb5c2140026c05b799bbeb67ad8470b3e93b70","tid":1995972,"uid":22068,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:35:52.000Z","msg":"疫情回穩反而睇淡殺定？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6a0571698bce01fbe6c635cd83ce2582a330d8","tid":1995972,"uid":121989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dafb5c2140026c05b799bbeb67ad8470b3e93b70","tid":1995972,"uid":22068,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:35:52.000Z","msg":"疫情回穩反而睇淡殺定？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:38:59.000Z","msg":"本月10號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"798d79e35f27d7b3ea498a0bcfcf434195027680","tid":1995972,"uid":199670,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3